                    <h2 class="block-title">Method Data</h2>
                  <div class="content">
        <div class="field field-name-field-min-participants field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Minimum Participants:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">1</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-max-participants field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Maximum Participants:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">No Maximim</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-min-duration field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Minimum Duration:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">No Minimum</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-max-duration field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Maximum Duration:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">No Maximum</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-participant-selection field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Participant Selection:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/method-recruitment/open-all" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Open to all</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-communication-mode field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Communication Mode:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/type-interaction-among-participants/discussion-dialogue-or-deliberation" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Discussion, Dialogue, or Deliberation</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/type-interaction-among-participants/negotiate-bargain" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Negotiate &amp; Bargain</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/type-interaction-among-participants/express-opinionspreferences-only" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Express opinions/preferences only</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/type-interaction-among-participants/listenwatch-spectator" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Listen/watch as spectator</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-public-interaction-method field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Public Interaction Method(s):&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Users pro and con lists are posted</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-decision-methods field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Decision Method(s):&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">User decisions are made through a stance slider tool</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-geographical-scope field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Geographical Scope:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/geographical-scope/regional-eg-state-province-autonomous-region" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Regional (e.g. State, Province, Autonomous Region)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-typical-funding-source field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Typical Funding Source:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/entities/national-government" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">National Government</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-governance-contributions field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Governance Contributions:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/governance-contributions/co-production" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Co-Production</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/governance-contributions/conflict-resolution" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Conflict Resolution</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/governance-contributions/decision-making" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Decision-Making</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-issue-polarization field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Issue Polarization:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/polarization/4-polarized" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">4 - Polarized</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-issue-complexity field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Issue Technical Complexity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/complexity/4-quite-complex" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">4 - Quite Complex</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-issue-interdependency field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Issue Interdependency	:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/interdependency/4-often-interdependent-other-issues" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">4 - Often Interdependent with Other Issues</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-influence-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Kind of Influence:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/kind-influence/raise-public-awareness" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Raise public awareness</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/kind-influence/community-building-eg-social-capital" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Community building (e.g. social capital)</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/kind-influence/develop-individual-capacities-eg-skills-learning" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Develop individual capacities (e.g. skills, learning)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-goods-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Best for:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/kind-goods/achieving-public-goods" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Achieving Public Goods</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/kind-goods/addressing-identity-based-issues" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Addressing Identity-Based Issues</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-facilitated field-type-list-boolean field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Facilitated:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">No</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-sponsoring-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Typical Sponsoring Entity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/entities/regional-government-eg-state-provincial-territorial" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Regional Government (e.g. State, Provincial, Territorial)</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/entities/academic-institution" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Academic Institution</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/entities/community-based-organization" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Community Based Organization</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-implementing-entity-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Typical Implementing Entity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/entities/academic-institution" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Academic Institution</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/entities/non-governmental-organization-non-profit" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Non-Governmental Organization (Non-profit)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-interaction-method field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Methods of Interaction:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Pro and Con lists</div></div></div>      </div>
      
